OL,3,CFamily pay tribute to 'deeply loved'
OL,4,Cgrandad who died at Seaton Carew
OL,6,FThe family of a man who died after
OL,7,Fentering the sea to help two children
OL,8,Fin difficulty have described the loss
OL,9,Fof said the loss they feel is
OL,10,F"immeasurable".
OL,12,FIan Pascoe, 62, from Peterlee in
OL,13,FCounty Durham, died on Sunday 12 July
OL,14,Fafter going into the sea at Seaton
OL,15,FCarew beach.
OL,17,FMr Pascoe's family described him as a
OL,18,F"beloved father, husband, brother and
OL,19,Fgrandad" and thanked the emergency
OL,20,Fservices who tried to save his life.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
