CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1784215104
OL,3,CFamily pay tribute to 'deeply loved'
OL,4,Cgrandad who died at Seaton Carew
OL,6,FEmergency services were called to
OL,7,FSeaton Carew beach at around 3.45pm on
OL,8,FSunday 12 July after two children got
OL,9,Finto difficulty in the water.
OL,11,FMr Pascoe and another man, Wayne
OL,12,FTaylor, entered the sea to help. The
OL,13,Fchildren were rescued and taken to
OL,14,Fhospital as a precaution.
OL,16,FIn a statement, Mr Pascoe's family
OL,17,Fsaid: "It is with profound sadness
OL,18,Fthat we confirm the death of our
OL,19,Fbeloved father, husband, brother and
OL,20,Fgrandad, Ian.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1784215104
OL,3,CFamily pay tribute to 'deeply loved'
OL,4,Cgrandad who died at Seaton Carew
OL,6,F"As a family, we would like to express
OL,7,Four sincere gratitude to the police,
OL,8,Fambulance service, Coastguard and RNLI
OL,9,Ffor their efforts, professionalism and
OL,10,Fcompassion throughout this incredibly
OL,11,Fdifficult time. We will always be
OL,12,Fgrateful to everyone involved.
OL,14,F"We have been truly humbled by the
OL,15,Foverwhelming response from members of
OL,16,Fthe public, so many of whom have
OL,17,Fclearly been touched and moved by this
OL,18,Ftragedy. The messages of sympathy,
OL,19,Fkindness and support have meant more
OL,20,Fto our family than we can adequately
OL,21,Fput into words.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1784215104
OL,3,CFamily pay tribute to 'deeply loved'
OL,4,Cgrandad who died at Seaton Carew
OL,6,F"Ian will forever remain in our
OL,7,Fhearts. He was deeply loved, and the
OL,8,Floss we feel is immeasurable.
OL,10,F"We will miss him always and carry his
OL,11,Fmemory with us for the rest of our
OL,12,Flives."
OL,14,FTwo other men, including Davey Short,
OL,15,Falso entered the sea to help during
OL,16,Fthe rescue and made it safely back to
OL,17,Fshore.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1784215104
OL,3,CFamily pay tribute to 'deeply loved'
OL,4,Cgrandad who died at Seaton Carew
OL,6,FMr Short said told ITV News Tyne Tees:
OL,7,F"I just wanted to get out there to
OL,8,Fhelp the little boy what was screaming
OL,9,F'help'. I just told him to swim
OL,10,Ftowards me, 'keep swimming towards
OL,11,Fus'. I managed to get to him and got
OL,12,Fhim out."
OL,14,FHe added: "I'm no hero, I just did
OL,15,Fwhat any man would do - or any dad.
OL,16,FAnd I would do it again today if I had
OL,17,Fto."
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1784215104
OL,3,CFamily pay tribute to 'deeply loved'
OL,4,Cgrandad who died at Seaton Carew
OL,6,FThe tragedy prompted an outpouring of
OL,7,Ftributes, with flowers left on the
OL,8,Fbeach in memory of the two men, who
OL,9,Fhave been described as "heroes" by the
OL,10,Flocal community.
OL,12,FIt has also sparked calls for improved
OL,13,Fwater safety measures along
OL,14,FHartlepool's coastline. More than
OL,15,F2,500 people signed a petition calling
OL,16,Ffor lifeguards to patrol the town's
OL,17,Fbeaches beyond the six-week school
OL,18,Fsummer holidays.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/7
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1784215104
OL,3,CFamily pay tribute to 'deeply loved'
OL,4,Cgrandad who died at Seaton Carew
OL,6,FHartlepool Borough Council has since
OL,7,Flaunched a review of water safety
OL,8,Fprovision along the coastline,
OL,9,Fincluding Seaton Carew, which will
OL,10,Fconsider lifeguard provision, signage,
OL,11,Feducation and prevention measures.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G7/7
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
